{"id": 2316, "genre": 1001, "title": "人际交往中，有哪一刻你觉得友谊破裂、做不成朋友了？", "description": "朋友分手大调查！“太不够意思了”到底是几个意思？（题图来自：视觉中国 ©️Vetta ）", "record_count": 5508, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20180507181342izyfLbks3GvmrTau.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2018-05-09T03:00:00Z", "options": [{"id": 280832, "content": "始终是单向的喋喋不休的无穷无尽的抱怨和负能量。", "image": null, "praise_count": 683, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 982279}, {"id": 281088, "content": "语言冷暴力，未经允许的花名，瞎起哄", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1277264}, {"id": 281344, "content": "都忘了你的时候，可能独自一人也蛮好。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340824}, {"id": 281600, "content": "年龄越大越没有朋友", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343916}, {"id": 280833, "content": "你最需要她们的时候，她们都不在身边。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 703760}, {"id": 280834, "content": "永远在你面前装作若无其事", "image": null, "praise_count": 10, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1289458}, {"id": 281090, "content": "眼神开始不对劲的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340118}, {"id": 281602, "content": "以朋友的身份做仇人的事！", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343921}, {"id": 282626, "content": "亲密接触这么久，忽然她说她喜欢女人", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 744519}, {"id": 280835, "content": "最好的朋友，背后说我坏话", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1258446}, {"id": 281091, "content": "猜疑", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1272810}, {"id": 280836, "content": "有事才找你，没事从不回消息", "image": null, "praise_count": 48, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1326444}, {"id": 281092, "content": "我本将心向明月，奈何明月照沟渠", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041215}, {"id": 281093, "content": "表面笑哈哈，底下捅你刀", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340124}, {"id": 280838, "content": "撒谎", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1278872}, {"id": 281094, "content": "有债务纠葛", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1329828}, {"id": 280839, "content": "大概是。。每次出去玩没有付钱的意识。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 51, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339417}, {"id": 280840, "content": "暗恋她，后来发现，她也喜欢姑娘", "image": null, "praise_count": 12, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 118850}, {"id": 281096, "content": "就是每次都是从别人口中听到她的故事", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1222497}, {"id": 280841, "content": "没钱的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339394}, {"id": 281097, "content": "突然间跟别人表白，别人不接受", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340133}, {"id": 281610, "content": "买奶茶要买十五块的，太贵了", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1343977}, {"id": 280843, "content": "开始跟你见外", "image": null, "praise_count": 36, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 92953}, {"id": 281099, "content": "突然凶我", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1291382}, {"id": 281355, "content": "距离变远，共同话题越来越少", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1154480}, {"id": 280844, "content": "她只是在利用你。", "image": null, "praise_count": 105, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1237927}, {"id": 281100, "content": "有没有一起玩爱情银行的23333", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1322762}, {"id": 280845, "content": "很明显的做对", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1163268}, {"id": 281101, "content": "每次他用你，黏你半天，你用他各种借口", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340149}, {"id": 281357, "content": "我把你当朋友，你特么想搞基?", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340884}, {"id": 280846, "content": "表面和你亲密 背后说你坏话 心机girl", "image": null, "praise_count": 167, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 658473}, {"id": 281102, "content": "忽然发现和她一起玩自己变得越来越差劲", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1315279}, {"id": 280847, "content": "你一直认为两人是铁杆，但是一般只有你找他，他从不主动找你，突然觉得这友谊维系的好累。", "image": null, "praise_count": 101, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1254638}, {"id": 281103, "content": "一起吃饭全是我给钱，我过生日的时候他给我打电话“今天你生日一起吃饭呗”，然后还是我付的钱。?", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 497766}, {"id": 280848, "content": "穷的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1339426}, {"id": 281104, "content": "发现自己在别人心里的位置后?", "image": null, "praise_count": 6, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340183}, {"id": 281360, "content": "被算计", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1333310}, {"id": 280849, "content": "我喜欢你", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1266221}, {"id": 281105, "content": "冷暴力", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340194}, {"id": 285969, "content": "生气了，不沟通，直接冷暴力", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1367616}, {"id": 280850, "content": "在自己感到无助时，给最好的朋友打电话说自己的难处。却得不到关心。第二天，看到空间上的说说，却和另外一堆的朋友去KTV唱歌，一副漠不关心。真的很想绝交", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1282247}, {"id": 280851, "content": "你结婚了我还单着", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 275723}, {"id": 280852, "content": "突然的冷漠  和突然的热情 ", "image": null, "praise_count": 173, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1337027}, {"id": 287764, "content": "兄弟，我突然发现我喜欢上你了???", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1377313}, {"id": 280853, "content": "不还钱", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 810883}, {"id": 281109, "content": "代购『你去xxxx（郊区）那个商场给我买，便宜』『咱俩你还收代购费』....", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1290657}, {"id": 280854, "content": "帮助了她很多，可等到需要的时候她连一个小忙都不帮", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1323654}, {"id": 281110, "content": "太自我的人，成不了朋友。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1340276}, {"id": 280855, "content": "情商低。", "image": null, "praise_count": 16, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1335505}, {"id": 280856, "content": "热评第一牛逼", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1208695}]}